# game/chapter4.rpy:1342
translate english chapter4_5_3d8780d2:

    # "어째서인지 좋은 울림으로 남은 그 한 마디가, 머릿속을 자꾸만 맴돌았다. "
    "That one sentence, which somehow stayed with me as a good echo, kept spinning in my head."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1348
translate english chapter4_5_b03cfcb5:

    # "같은 방향으로 20분 정도를 걸어, 현지는 “알아낸 게 생기면 다음번엔 꼭 연락해줘야 돼요?”라는 당부를 건네고선 내게 손을 흔들었다. "
    "After walking in the same direction for about 20 minutes, Hyeonji said \"You have to contact me if you find out anything, okay?\" and waved at me."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1351
translate english chapter4_5_33f2c1f5:

    # "그 뒤로 며칠간, 나는 소녀와 함께 리스트에 적혀 있던 장소를 돌아다녔다. "
    "For the next few days, I went around the places on the list with the girl."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1353
translate english chapter4_5_68c648a3:

    # "죽음을 마주한다는 지극히 비일상적인 일은 어느덧 일상처럼 변해있었고, 확인해야 할 장소 리스트에는 취소선이 하나둘씩 그여갔다. "
    "The very unusual thing of facing death had soon become like a routine, and the list of places to check had one or two lines crossed out."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1357
translate english chapter4_5_d8b44f5e:

    # "늘어만 가는 취소선과는 달리, 상황은 제자리걸음을 반복하는 것에 가까웠다. "
    "Unlike the growing lines, the situation was close to repeating itself in place."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1358
translate english chapter4_5_fbded395:

    # "물론 알아낸 것이 아예 없는 건 아니었다. "
    "Of course, it wasn't that I didn't find out anything at all."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1365
translate english chapter4_5_6b0a161b:

    # "첫 번째로는 소녀가 이야기했던 그 ‘따뜻한 사람’이란, 그녀 또래 정도 나이의 학생이었다는 것. "
    "The first thing was that the 'warm person' that the girl had talked about was a student of her age."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1366
translate english chapter4_5_9ab9a652:

    # "그리고 두 번째로는 이젠 소녀가 내 손을 잡는 데에 완전히 익숙해진 듯하다는 것. "
    "And the second thing was that she seemed to be completely used to holding my hand now."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1367
translate english chapter4_5_2ef2e3da:

    # "문제라면 그 두 가지가 며칠간 알아낸 것의 전부라는 거지만. "
    "The problem was that those two things were all I had found out in a few days."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1373
translate english chapter4_5_4bb9d192:

    # "그날은 D구역 외곽 지역에 있는 소각장을 둘러보기로 한 날이었다. "
    "That day was the day we decided to look around the crematorium in the outskirts of D district."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1374
translate english chapter4_5_9df4c24a:

    # "길을 찾는 데 조금 헤매는 바람에 해가 넘어가기 시작할 무렵이 되어서야 도착한 소각장에서, 소녀는 익숙한 듯 죽음의 자취를 좇아 소각장을 거닐었다. "
    "We arrived at the crematorium when the sun was starting to set, after getting a little lost on the way. The girl walked around the crematorium, following the traces of death as if she was familiar with them."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1375
translate english chapter4_5_3f3e6d73:

    # "나는 그런 소녀의 뒤를 따라 평범하기 그지없는 소각장의 풍경을 관망했다. "
    "I followed behind her and watched the ordinary scenery of the crematorium."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1376
translate english chapter4_5_43844056:

    # "얼마 정도 걸었을까, 소녀의 걸음이 멈췄다. "
    "After a while, the girl's steps stopped."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1378
translate english chapter4_5_b306c760:

    # "소녀의 발걸음이 멈춘 곳은 어느 한 소각로 앞에서였다. "
    "The place where the girl stopped was in front of one of the incinerators."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1380
translate english chapter4_5_58d035f6:

    # "소녀는 갑자기 소각로 위로 올라서더니, 그곳에서 허공을 빤히 응시했다. "
    "The girl suddenly climbed up on the incinerator and stared at the air intently."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1381
translate english chapter4_5_8acf9d81:

    # "분명 죽음의 색을 바라보고 있는 거겠지. "
    "She must be looking at the color of death."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1382
translate english chapter4_5_0d15ec54:

    # "그리고 이곳은 사고가 일어났던 소각로였던 것이고 말이다. "
    "And this was the incinerator where the accident had occurred."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1386
translate english chapter4_5_e958059b:

    # voice "voices/gd1.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“돌아가요.”"
    voice "voices/gd1.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Let's go back.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:1388
translate english chapter4_5_d15787ea:

    # voice ""
    # "소각로 위에 서서 몇 분 정도 생각에 잠겨있던 소녀가 나를 바라보며 힘없이 말했다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl looked at me and said weakly, after standing on the incinerator and being lost in thought for a few minutes."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1390
translate english chapter4_5_6f30ebd2:

    # "이번에도 딱히 떠오르는 것이 없다는, 함축적인 표현이었다. "
    "It was an implicit expression that she didn't have anything to come up with this time either."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1392
translate english chapter4_5_fd185aa9:

    # 나 "“아무것도 기억 안 나는가 보네.”"
    나 "\"I guess you don't remember anything.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:1397
translate english chapter4_5_6dd27856:

    # voice "voices/gd2.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 네.”"
    voice "voices/gd2.ogg"
    소녀 "\"...... Yes.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:1400
translate english chapter4_5_419c5f0a:

    # voice ""
    # "이번에도 알아낸 건 헛걸음을 했다는 사실뿐인 걸까. "
    voice ""
    "Did I only find out that I wasted my time this time too?"

# game/chapter4.rpy:1402
translate english chapter4_5_5cb4817b:

    # "이걸로 아무런 소득 없이 돌아다닌 장소만 해도 벌써 연달아 다섯 곳이었다. "
    "This was already the fifth place I had been wandering around without any gain."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1403
translate english chapter4_5_fa876216:

    # "돌아가자는 이야기를 꺼내려다 말고, 나는 이쪽을 향하는 소녀의 시선을 느끼고는 고개를 들었다. "
    "I was about to say let's go back, but I felt the girl's gaze toward me and lifted my head."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1405
translate english chapter4_5_24013353:

    # "나도 모르게 답답하다는 표정이라도 짓고 있었던 걸까. "
    "Did I unknowingly make a frustrated expression?"

# game/chapter4.rpy:1406
translate english chapter4_5_3dd3c676:

    # "소각로 위에 서서는 나를 내려다보고 있던 소녀가 나의 눈치를 조심스레 살피고 있었다. "
    "The girl who was standing on the incinerator and looking down at me was cautiously watching my mood."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1407
translate english chapter4_5_b43a6513:

    # "한참을 걸었는데도 불구하고 상황은 여전히 제자리걸음이라는 사실이 답답하게 느껴졌는지, 아니면 정점을 찍은 여름날의 후텁지근한 날씨가 나를 답답하게 만들었는지는 모르겠지만. "
    "I didn't know if it was because I felt frustrated that the situation was still at a standstill despite walking for a long time, or because the sultry weather of the summer day that had reached its peak made me feel suffocated."

# game/chapter4.rpy:1408
translate english chapter4_5_a1fec32a:

    # "의식을 하고 보니 무의식중에 찡그린 표정을 짓고 있었던 것 같기도 했다. "
    "When I became conscious of it, it seemed like I was unconsciously making a grimace."

