# game/chapter4.rpy:3116
translate english ecg8_label_d5f56d35:

    # "아니, 어쩌면 애초부터 현지에게 기대는 쪽이 플랜 A였는지도 모르고……. "
    "Or maybe relying on Hyeonji was plan A from the beginning..."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3118
translate english ecg8_label_64ee7c01:

    # voice "voices/gd85.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아뇨, 그게 아니라…… 보이지 않았거든요. 죽음의 색 말이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gd85.ogg"
    소녀 "\"No, that's not it... I didn't see it. The color of death, I mean.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3120
translate english ecg8_label_f5d0c2c7:

    # voice ""
    # "잠시 다른 생각을 하고 있던 내게 소녀는 자신의 이야기를 정정하듯 말을 덧붙였다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl added to her story as if to correct herself to me, who was thinking of something else for a moment."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3125
translate english ecg8_label_436b5755:

    # "그런가. "
    "I see."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3126
translate english ecg8_label_d9d76987:

    # "여기도 아닌 것이 아니라, 소녀는 여기가 아니라고 이야기하고 싶었던 거였다. "
    "It wasn't that it wasn't here, but that the girl wanted to say that it wasn't here."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3127
translate english ecg8_label_08a05824:

    # "여기서부터 상황은 예상 밖의 전개로 흘러가고 있었다. "
    "From here on, the situation was going in an unexpected direction."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3132
translate english ecg8_label_3b6e57d5:

    # 나 "“…… 잘못 본 거 아냐? 실수로 놓쳤다거나.”"
    나 "\"... Are you sure you didn't see it wrong? Or missed it by mistake.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3133
translate english ecg8_label_a3921151:

    # voice "voices/gd86.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그럴 리는 없어요.”"
    voice "voices/gd86.ogg"
    소녀 "\"There's no way that could happen.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3135
translate english ecg8_label_75ee3fd1:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“음…… 하긴, 여태껏 그런 적은 없었지.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Hmm... Well, yeah, you never did that before.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3137
translate english ecg8_label_e6a776c1:

    # voice "voices/gd87.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그래서 말인데요, 정말 여기가 맞는 건가요?”"
    voice "voices/gd87.ogg"
    소녀 "\"So, are you sure this is the right place?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3139
translate english ecg8_label_313f2058:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“확실해. 실종 신고된 여학생의 시체가 이곳에서 발견됐다는 뉴스가 났었으니까.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I'm sure. There was a news that the body of a missing female student was found here.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3141
translate english ecg8_label_8b470e2e:

    # voice "voices/gd88.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“혹시 모르니까, 강줄기를 따라 올라가 보는 건 어떨까요?”"
    voice "voices/gd88.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Just in case, how about we go up along the river?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3143
translate english ecg8_label_df6b2a54:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“요컨대, 너는 그 여학생이 죽은 곳이 여기가 아닐지도 모른다는 이야기를 하고 싶은 거지?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"In other words, you want to say that maybe this is not where that female student died?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3145
translate english ecg8_label_8e567597:

    # voice "voices/gd89.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 확실하진 않아요.”"
    voice "voices/gd89.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... I'm not sure.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3147
translate english ecg8_label_340a9154:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“뭐, 알겠어. 그렇게 하자.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Well, okay. Let's do that.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3153
translate english ecg8_label_f8eb071d:

    # "말끝을 흐리는 소녀였지만, 충분히 가능성 있는 추측이라 생각했다. "
    "The girl trailed off her words, but I thought it was a plausible guess."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3154
translate english ecg8_label_c2828afe:

    # "오히려 그 여학생의 시신이 상류에서 하구까지 떠내려왔을지도 모른다는 생각을 하지 않은 것이 이상하게 여겨질 정도였다. "
    "It was rather strange that I didn't think that the body of that female student might have drifted down from the upper reaches to the estuary."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3158
translate english ecg8_label_7859dcd0:

    # "강의 상류 쪽을 향해 길을 따라 걸어갔다. "
    "I walked along the road towards the upper part of the river."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3159
translate english ecg8_label_6f991e91:

    # "소녀는 길을 걸어 올라가며 열심히 강변을 살폈다. "
    "The girl looked carefully at the riverside as she walked up the road."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3160
translate english ecg8_label_7e86d9b9:

    # "물살의 폭이 줄어들기 시작하고, 맞닿은 하늘과 어울리는 색을 찾아가고 있었다. "
    "The force of the water began to decrease, and it was looking for a color that matched the sky it touched."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3164
translate english ecg8_label_d37495bf:

    # voice "voices/gd90.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그 여학생의 사인은 뭐였나요?”"
    voice "voices/gd90.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What was the cause of death of that female student?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3166
translate english ecg8_label_069849ad:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“사고사라고만 되어 있어. 직접적인 원인은 아마도 익사겠지.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It only said it was an accident. The direct cause was probably drowning.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3168
translate english ecg8_label_ecb26ca8:

    # voice "voices/gd91.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“다른 이야기는 없었나요?”"
    voice "voices/gd91.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Was there any other story?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3170
translate english ecg8_label_897b3829:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“혹시 자살이 아니었을까 하는 이야기도 있었는데, 경찰 쪽에선 사고사로 결론 내린 모양이야.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"There was also a story that maybe it wasn't a suicide, but the police seemed to conclude it was an accident.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3172
translate english ecg8_label_ecdd6d9e:

    # voice "voices/gd92.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“음…… 그렇군요.”"
    voice "voices/gd92.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Hmm... I see.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3175
translate english ecg8_label_2f596927:

    # voice ""
    # "강의 중상류쯤에 도착해, 나와 소녀는 가볍게 숨을 돌렸다. "
    voice ""
    "We arrived at the middle-upper part of the river and took a light breath."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3180
translate english ecg8_label_1d397361:

    # 나 "“어때? 보이는 게 있어?”"
    나 "\"How about it? Do you see anything?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3181
translate english ecg8_label_3bab0259:

    # voice "voices/gd93.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아뇨, 아무것도요.”"
    voice "voices/gd93.ogg"
    소녀 "\"No, nothing.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3183
translate english ecg8_label_56ad0fa7:

    # voice ""
    # "다시 가던 길을 걸어가려다 말고, 나는 마침 근처에 있던 벤치를 가리켰다. "
    voice ""
    "I was about to walk back the way we came, but I pointed to a bench that was nearby."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3188
translate english ecg8_label_3b14fd07:

    # 나 "“저기, 벤치에서 잠깐 쉬었다 갈래?”"
    나 "\"Hey, do you want to take a break on the bench for a while?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3189
translate english ecg8_label_a5c2b886:

    # voice "voices/gd94.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“좋아요.”"
    voice "voices/gd94.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Sure.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3194
translate english ecg8_label_f398a7b6:

    # voice ""
    # "벤치 옆에 놓여있는 자판기에서 캔음료를 뽑아 소녀에게 건넸다. "
    voice ""
    "I took a canned drink from the vending machine next to the bench and handed it to the girl. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3199
translate english ecg8_label_8ad1a182:

    # voice "voices/gd95.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“감사합니다.”"
    voice "voices/gd95.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Thank you.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3204
translate english ecg8_label_52a15f06:

    # voice ""
    # "내게서 음료를 받아든 소녀는 벤치에 앉아 강과 하늘이 이루는 장면을 감상하며 캔을 비웠다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl who took the drink from me sat on the bench and emptied the can while admiring the scene of the river and the sky. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3206
translate english ecg8_label_4fc3c4ec:

    # "적당히 숨을 고를 동안, 나는 소녀의 옆에 앉아 태블릿을 켜 뉴스 기사를 찾기 시작했다. "
    "While I caught my breath, I sat next to the girl and turned on the tablet to look for news articles. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3207
translate english ecg8_label_70aa4289:

    # "무선 네트워크가 원활하게 잡히지는 않았지만, 그래도 뉴스 기사를 검색할 정도로는 충분했다. "
    "The wireless network was not very smooth, but it was enough to search for news articles. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3216
translate english ecg8_label_eb458414:

    # 나 "“그 여학생의 사망 추정 일자는 8월 16일, 그리고 시신이 발견된 일자는 8월 22일이야. 발견되었을 때 시신은 이미 형체를 알아보기 힘들 정도로 물에 불어 있어서 제대로 된 부검은 진행하지 못했대.” "
    나 "\"The estimated date of death of the female student is August 16th, and the date when the body was found is August 22nd. When it was found, the body was already swollen by water to the point where it was hard to recognize its shape, so they couldn't conduct a proper autopsy.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3218
translate english ecg8_label_4e381b8d:

    # 나 "“그리고 이 여학생이 실종되었던 16일과 20일 사이에 긴 비가 내렸던 것 같아. 비가 엄청 많이 와서, 아마 이쪽 부근 길을 걷다 실족사했을 거라고 결론을 내렸나 봐.”"
    나 "\"And it seems that there was a long rain between the 16th and 20th when this female student went missing. It rained so much that they concluded that she probably slipped and died while walking along this side of the road.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3224
translate english ecg8_label_625e7c6c:

    # voice "voices/gd96.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이상해요. 그렇다면 지금쯤 죽음의 색을 발견해야 했을 거라고요.”"
    voice "voices/gd96.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's strange. Then you should have found the color of death by now.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3229
translate english ecg8_label_56a383a9:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 음료를 한 모금 마시고는 이야기를 이어갔다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl took a sip of her drink and continued her story. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3231
translate english ecg8_label_2731dc06:

    # voice "voices/gd97.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“있잖아요, 이건 제 추측일 뿐이지만……. 세 가지 가능성이 있다고 생각해요.”"
    voice "voices/gd97.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You know, this is just my guess, but...... I think there are three possibilities.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3233
translate english ecg8_label_f1ed0a92:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어떤 건데?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"What are they?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3238
translate english ecg8_label_5ea09aba:

    # voice "voices/gd98.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“먼저 첫 번째 가능성은, 그 여학생이 죽은 장소가 이곳이 아니었다는 거예요.”"
    voice "voices/gd98.ogg"
    소녀 "\"The first possibility is that the place where the female student died was not here.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3240
translate english ecg8_label_630cc6c8:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“여기가 아니라면…… 여기에서 멀리 떨어진 곳을 생각하고 있기라도 한 거야?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"If it's not here...... are you thinking of a place far away from here?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3242
translate english ecg8_label_999adae5:

    # voice "voices/gd99.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“네. 어디인지는 알 수 없지만요.”"
    voice "voices/gd99.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Yes. I don't know where, though.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3244
translate english ecg8_label_41b6687e:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“하지만 그 여학생의 시체는 분명 강 하구에서 발견되었잖아.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"But the body of the female student was clearly found at the river mouth.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3246
translate english ecg8_label_a330b155:

    # voice "voices/gd100.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그렇죠.”"
    voice "voices/gd100.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's right.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3248
translate english ecg8_label_425b0f59:

    # voice ""
    # "마치 내게 잠시 생각할 시간을 주려는 듯, 소녀가 이야기를 멈추었다. "
    voice ""
    "As if to give me some time to think, the girl stopped talking. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3250
translate english ecg8_label_b41d56e0:

    # "나는 태블릿을 내려놓고선 소녀가 풀어 놓았던 이야기들을 조립해 나갔다. "
    "I put down the tablet and assembled the stories that the girl had told me. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3252
translate english ecg8_label_c0911a04:

    # 나 "“즉, 누군가가 그 여학생의 시체를 몰래 강에 버렸을 가능성을 생각하고 있는 거네.”"
    나 "\"In other words, you're thinking of the possibility that someone secretly dumped the body of the female student into the river.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3253
translate english ecg8_label_6d3010ce:

    # voice "voices/gd101.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“추측일 뿐이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gd101.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's just a guess.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3256
translate english ecg8_label_46590a36:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 그렇게 자신의 의견을 일축하고는 다음 이야기로 넘어갔다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl downplayed her opinion and moved on to the next story. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3259
translate english ecg8_label_3126e804:

    # voice "voices/gd102.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“두 번째 가능성은, 여기서 발견된 시신이 바로 저일 수도 있다는 거예요.”"
    voice "voices/gd102.ogg"
    소녀 "\"The second possibility is that the body found here could be me.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3261
translate english ecg8_label_29c66513:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 어떤 이유에서?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...... For what reason?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3263
translate english ecg8_label_9713587d:

    # voice "voices/gd103.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“말 그대로 가능성일 뿐이에요. 하지만 만약 그 여학생이 정말 이 부근에서 실족사한 것이 맞다면, 죽음의 색이 보이지 않을 이유는 달리 없으니까요. 어쩌면 저는 제 자신이 만들어낸 죽음의 색은 보지 못하는 걸지도 모르죠.”"
    voice "voices/gd103.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's just a possibility. But if the female student really died from slipping in this area, there's no other reason why I can't see the color of death. Maybe I can't see the color of death that I created myself.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3266
translate english ecg8_label_04ed8297:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아아, 그래서 아까 사고 현장이 여기가 아닐지도 모른다고 했을 때 확실하지 않다고 얼버무렸던 거구나.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Ah, so that's why you weren't sure when you said the accident scene might not be here.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3272
translate english ecg8_label_fde0b173:

    # "소녀는 고개를 끄덕였다. "
    "The girl nodded her head. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3274
translate english ecg8_label_6143a639:

    # 나 "“그럼 마지막 가능성은 뭐야?”"
    나 "\"Then what's the last possibility?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3277
translate english ecg8_label_9ac75ad6:

    # voice "voices/gd104.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“위의 두 가지 가능성이 {color=#00ccff}동시에{/color} 만족하는 거예요.”"
    voice "voices/gd104.ogg"
    소녀 "\"The two possibilities above are {color=#00ccff}both{/color} satisfied.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3279
translate english ecg8_label_bee27395:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 동시에?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...... Both?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3285
translate english ecg8_label_1cb4217c:

    # voice "voices/gd105.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“네. 동시에.”"
    voice "voices/gd105.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Yes. Both.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3289
translate english ecg8_label_ba105d33:

    # voice ""
    # "그렇다는 건, 소녀는 누군가에게 살해당한 뒤 강에 버려졌다는 걸까. "
    voice ""
    "Does that mean that the girl was killed by someone and then dumped into the river? "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3291
translate english ecg8_label_3360ad9f:

    # "머릿속에서 일련의 가설들이 하나하나 조립되기 시작했다. "
    "A series of hypotheses began to assemble in my head one by one. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3298
translate english ecg8_label_82235138:

    # "소녀의 시신은 뒤늦게 경찰에게 발견되어 조사가 시작되었지만, 진범을 찾지 못한 채 사고사로 결론나게 된다. "
    "The girl's body was belatedly discovered by the police and an investigation began, but the culprit was not found and it was concluded as an accident."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3300
translate english ecg8_label_64b37a7a:

    # "사건의 진상을 밝히지 못한 것이 억울함으로 남아있던 소녀는 그 원한으로 이곳을 떠도는 유령이 되어버렸다. "
    "The girl, who was left with a sense of injustice for not being able to reveal the truth of the incident, became a ghost wandering around this place with her grudge. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3302
translate english ecg8_label_3aa5873d:

    # "그런 이야기일까? "
    "Is that the story? "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3306
translate english ecg8_label_e547dbc4:

    # "모든 것이 톱니바퀴처럼 딱딱 맞아떨어졌다. "
    "Everything fit together like a cogwheel. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3307
translate english ecg8_label_e0f6ce2b:

    # "마치, 여태껏 있었던 일들이 모두 지금을 위해 일어난 것처럼. "
    "As if, everything that had happened so far was for this moment. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3309
translate english ecg8_label_712ccfa8:

    # 나 "“그렇다고 한다면, 네가 유령이 된 이유도 어쩌면 설명이 될지 몰라.”"
    나 "\"If that's the case, maybe your reason for becoming a ghost can be explained too.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3311
translate english ecg8_label_5fc77e43:

    # voice "voices/gd106.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그저 가능성일 뿐이에요. 아주 희박한 가능성.”"
    voice "voices/gd106.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's just a possibility. A very slim possibility.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3314
translate english ecg8_label_b2750904:

    # voice ""
    # "오래간만의 진전에, 내 목소리가 약간은 감정적인 어조를 띠었다. "
    voice ""
    "With the long-awaited breakthrough, my voice took on a slightly emotional tone. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3317
translate english ecg8_label_64a08e91:

    # "그에 반해 소녀는 여전히 차분함을 잃지 않은 채 자신의 추측에 신중함을 기하고 있었다. "
    "In contrast, the girl remained calm and cautious about her speculation. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3318
translate english ecg8_label_81c97699:

    # "나는 환상 속을 걷듯 추측을 계속 이어 나갔다. "
    "I continued to follow the conjecture as if walking in a delusion. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3322
translate english ecg8_label_a1c9cb51:

    # "소녀가 유령이 된 이유가 진상이 규명되지 않은 억울한 죽음이라 한다면, 나는 소녀의 억울함을 풀어줘야만 하는 걸까? "
    "If the reason why the girl became a ghost was her unjust death that was not clarified, would I have to relieve her of her injustice? "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3323
translate english ecg8_label_a782cf3b:

    # "하지만 사건은 이미 종결되었고, 난데없이 1년 전 여름에 있었던 사고가 실은 살인 사건이라는 이야기를 해봤자 믿어주는 사람이 있을 리가 없다. "
    "But the case was already closed, and there was no way anyone would believe me if I suddenly said that the accident that happened in the summer of a year ago was actually a murder case."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3325
translate english ecg8_label_3cca3627:

    # 나 "“만약 그렇다면 내가 할 수 있는 일이 뭐가 있을까? 진범을 찾는 일?”"
    나 "\"If that's the case, what can I do? Finding the culprit?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3329
translate english ecg8_label_d9e66b61:

    # voice "voices/gd107.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그런 위험한 일은 생각도 하지 않는 편이 나아요.”"
    voice "voices/gd107.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's better not to think about such a dangerous thing.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3332
translate english ecg8_label_e12ec606:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 꽤나 단호한 어조로 나의 말을 가로막았다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl cut off my words with a rather firm tone. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3334
translate english ecg8_label_57779584:

    # "하지만 그녀의 목소리에서는 미묘한 떨림이 느껴졌다. "
    "But I felt a subtle tremor in her voice. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3339
translate english ecg8_label_1c94ceff:

    # voice "voices/gd108.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 그치만, 억울하겠죠? {color=#00ccff}누군가에게 살해당했는데, 그 사람은 죗값조차 치르지 않고 멀쩡히 살아있다면.{/color}”"
    voice "voices/gd108.ogg"
    소녀 "\"...... But, it would be unfair, right? {color=#00ccff}If someone killed you, and that person is living well without paying for their sin.{/color}\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3341
translate english ecg8_label_bc7cc408:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“죽은 사람은 말이 없지만. 그렇겠지.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"The dead have no voice. I guess so.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3349
translate english ecg8_label_e06343d0:

    # "그때는 알지 못했던 것 같다. "
    "I didn't seem to know then. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3350
translate english ecg8_label_8ff8f007:

    # "그 질문이 그토록 중요한 질문이었을 줄은. "
    "How important that question was. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3352
translate english ecg8_label_0721fff3:

    # "벤치에서 일어나려다 말고, 소녀가 몸을 휘청였다. "
    "As I was about to get up from the bench, the girl staggered. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3353
translate english ecg8_label_c626b065:

    # "넘어질 뻔한 소녀에게 손을 뻗었지만, 소녀는 금세 균형을 되찾았다. "
    "I reached out to the girl who almost fell, but she quickly regained her balance. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3357
translate english ecg8_label_749a891e:

    # 나 "“…… 왜 그래?”"
    나 "\"... What's up?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3358
translate english ecg8_label_4d5630d2:

    # voice "voices/gd109.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그냥 살짝 현기증이 난 것뿐이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gd109.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's just a little dizziness.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3360
translate english ecg8_label_35de7a08:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“괜찮은 거야?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Are you okay?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3362
translate english ecg8_label_a2e1a4fa:

    # voice "voices/gd110.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“조금만 더 걸어요. 괜찮을까요?”"
    voice "voices/gd110.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Let's walk a little more. Is that okay?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3368
translate english ecg8_label_0f871c1e:

    # voice ""
    # "벤치에서 몸을 일으키자, 소녀가 나의 손을 잡았다. "
    voice ""
    "As I got up from the bench, the girl grabbed my hand. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3370
translate english ecg8_label_e217c93b:

    # "강변을 따라 걸으며, 우리는 점점 거칠게 흘러가는 물줄기를 유심히 바라보았다. "
    "Walking along the river, we looked closely at the increasingly rough stream. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3371
translate english ecg8_label_a51209e9:

    # "소녀는 아무래도 죽음의 흔적 같은 건 이곳에서 찾을 수 없었는지 이따금 기분을 전환하려는 듯 심호흡을 내쉬었다. "
    "The girl seemed to have failed to find any traces of death here, and occasionally sighed deeply as if to change her mood. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3376
translate english ecg8_label_6a3fbdd1:

    # "소녀의 체온과 숨결이 나에게 전해지는 순간이었다. "
    "It was the moment when the girl's body temperature and breath reached me. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3380
translate english ecg8_label_a9412c1e:

    # "40분 정도를 걸어 결국 수원지까지 도착해버린 우리는 그곳에서 잠시 시간을 보내기로 했다. "
    "After walking for about 40 minutes, we finally reached the source and decided to spend some time there. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3381
translate english ecg8_label_cb615aa9:

    # "수원지는 말 그대로 칙칙함으로 물들어 있었다. "
    "The source was literally dyed with dullness. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3382
translate english ecg8_label_ecbe1be4:

    # "풀도, 나무도 보이지 않는 돌 더미로 이루어진 공간 속에서 그나마 드문드문 보이는 이끼들이 푸르죽죽한 색을 발했다. "
    "In a space made of piles of rocks with no grass or trees in sight, the mosses that were sparsely visible emitted a greenish color. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3383
translate english ecg8_label_8bd170fb:

    # "앉아있을 만한 평평한 바위를 찾은 우리는 그곳에 앉아 이런저런 잡담을 나누었다. "
    "We found a flat rock to sit on and chatted about this and that."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3384
translate english ecg8_label_b61e960a:

    # "시간을 때우는 것이기도 했고, 시간이 흘러가고 있다는 것을 잠깐이나마 잊는 것이기도 했다. "
    "It was both a way to pass the time and a way to forget for a moment that time was passing. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3390
translate english ecg8_label_d3806294:

    # 나 "“현기증은 이제 좀 괜찮아?”"
    나 "\"Are you feeling better from the dizziness?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3392
translate english ecg8_label_22375372:

    # voice "voices/gd111.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“바람을 쐬니까 괜찮아졌어요.”"
    voice "voices/gd111.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I feel better after getting some fresh air.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3394
translate english ecg8_label_a1b75147:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“다행이네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"That's good.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3400
translate english ecg8_label_5081f1d5:

    # "아까보다는 한결 가벼워진 목소리로 소녀가 말했다. "
    "The girl spoke with a much lighter voice than before. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3401
translate english ecg8_label_3498f923:

    # "나를 기준으로 동쪽에 위치해 있던 구름 한 조각이 서쪽으로 옮겨갔을 때쯤, 소녀의 시선이 어디엔가 고정되었다. "
    "Around the time when a piece of cloud that was east of me moved to the west, the girl's gaze fixed somewhere. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3406
translate english ecg8_label_c578e2e5:

    # "소녀를 따라 시선이 향한 곳에는, 한 마리의 길고양이가 두어 발짝 건너에서 우리를 바라보고 있었다. "
    "Following the girl's gaze, there was a stray cat looking at us a few steps away. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3412
translate english ecg8_label_1a90d311:

    # voice "voices/gd112.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“저기 봐요, 고양이예요.”"
    voice "voices/gd112.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Look, it's a cat.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3414
translate english ecg8_label_5874a676:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“정말이네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It really is.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3417
translate english ecg8_label_db8e871e:

    # "별도 보이지 않는 새까만 밤하늘을 연상케 하는 색으로 뒤덮인 고양이었다. "
    "It was a cat covered in a color that reminded me of the black night sky that was not visible elsewhere."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3418
translate english ecg8_label_3283b6fe:

    # "미래로 넘어온 뒤로 길고양이를 보는 것은 아마 지금이 처음인 것 같았다. "
    "I think this was the first time I saw a stray cat after coming to the future."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3419
translate english ecg8_label_1ef55832:

    # "유령이 되어 버린 소녀도 그건 매한가지였는지, 반짝이는 시선이 고양이를 향하고 있었다. "
    "The girl who had become a ghost also seemed to be the same, her sparkling eyes were directed at the cat. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3420
translate english ecg8_label_ed72ed26:

    # "그런 소녀와 고양이를 바라보고 있자니 문득 궁금한 게 생겼다. "
    "As I looked at the girl and the cat, I suddenly became curious. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3423
translate english ecg8_label_31ab9792:

    # 나 "“그런데 고양이는 널 볼 수 있어?”"
    나 "\"But can the cat see you?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3425
translate english ecg8_label_5df70a03:

    # voice "voices/gd113.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“글쎄요. 잠깐만요.”"
    voice "voices/gd113.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I don't know. Wait a minute.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3434
translate english ecg8_label_6418f853:

    # voice ""
    # "앉아있던 바위에서 폴짝 뛰어내린 소녀는 조심조심 고양이를 향해 다가갔다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl jumped off the rock where she was sitting and cautiously approached the cat. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3436
translate english ecg8_label_17706a25:

    # "눈치를 채지 못한 건지, 사람에 대한 경계심이 없는 건지, 고양이는 그 자리에서 이곳을 계속 바라보았다. "
    "Whether it didn't notice or had no fear of people, the cat kept looking at this place from where it was. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3444
translate english ecg8_label_215d4eb0:

    # "어느새 고양이 곁으로 다가간 소녀는 고양이 앞에서 손을 흔들어 보였다. "
    "The girl who had reached the cat's side waved her hand in front of the cat. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3451
translate english ecg8_label_a1d9b576:

    # "고양이는 아무런 반응을 보이지 않았다. "
    "The cat showed no reaction. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3459
translate english ecg8_label_1404eba3:

    # "그저 갸르릉거리는 소리를 내며 앞발로 자신의 뺨을 매만지기만 할 뿐. "
    "It just made a purring sound and rubbed its cheek with its front paw."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3460
translate english ecg8_label_3758753e:

    # voice "voices/gd114.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“고양이도 제가 안 보이는 것 같아요.”"
    voice "voices/gd114.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It seems like the cat can't see me either.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3473
translate english ecg9_label_1eeb6978:

    # voice ""
    # "고양이가 자신을 보지 못한다는 것을 확인한 소녀는 손을 뻗더니 고양이를 껴안아 들어 올렸다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl who confirmed that the cat couldn't see her reached out and hugged the cat."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3475
translate english ecg9_label_0a6e09bf:

    # "이번에도 고양이는 별다른 반응을 보이지 않았다. "
    "The cat didn't show any reaction this time either. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3476
translate english ecg9_label_34901dba:

    # voice "voices/gd115.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“고양이는 이런 촉감이었군요.”"
    voice "voices/gd115.ogg"
    소녀 "\"So this is what a cat feels like.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3478
translate english ecg9_label_75853d29:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“처음 만져보는 거야?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Is this your first time touching one?\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3480
translate english ecg9_label_e1bded01:

    # voice "voices/gd116.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“말했잖아요. 살아 있었을 땐 고양이들이 저만 보면 도망갔었다고요.”"
    voice "voices/gd116.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I told you. When I was alive, the cats ran away as soon as they saw me.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3482
translate english ecg9_label_e195a09a:

    # voice ""
    # "아까까지만 해도 약간 가라앉아 있던 소녀의 목소리에는 활기가 깃돌았다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl's voice, which had been slightly subdued until now, was filled with vitality. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3484
translate english ecg9_label_a69fbc86:

    # "소녀는 여태껏 고양이를 만져보지 못했던 한을 풀듯 마음껏 고양이를 쓰다듬었다. "
    "The girl stroked the cat as much as she could, as if to vent her frustration of not being able to touch a cat before. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3485
translate english ecg9_label_0abc349f:

    # "머지않아 성불을 할지도 모른다는 생각이 들 정도로 행복해 보이는 얼굴이었다. "
    "She looked so happy that I thought she might burst into flames soon."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3486
translate english ecg9_label_a177c5fc:

    # voice "voices/gd117.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“푹신푹신할 줄 알았는데, 약간 까슬까슬하네요.”"
    voice "voices/gd117.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I thought it would be fluffy, but it's a bit rough.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3488
translate english ecg9_label_1050cab6:

    # voice ""
    # "뿌듯함을 잔뜩 담아, 소녀는 고양이를 만져본 소감을 말했다. "
    voice ""
    "With a proud expression, the girl told me her impression of touching the cat."

# game/chapter4.rpy:3490
translate english ecg9_label_009d9962:

    # voice "voices/gd118.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“유령이 되어서 나쁜 점만 있는 건 아닌 것 같아요.”"
    voice "voices/gd118.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Being a ghost doesn't seem to be all bad.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3492
translate english ecg9_label_45b882a3:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“애써 유령이 되었을 때의 좋은 점을 찾은 것 같네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It seems like you're trying to find the good side of being a ghost.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3497
translate english ecg9_label_6409da4b:

    # voice "voices/gd119.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그런 안쓰러운 눈빛으로 쳐다보지 마세요.”"
    voice "voices/gd119.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Don't look at me with such a pitiful look.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3499
translate english ecg9_label_fd7e4175:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어라, 그렇게 보였다면 미안.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Oh, sorry if I looked like that.\""

# game/chapter4.rpy:3502
translate english ecg9_label_d22f803f:

    # "나는 고양이와 함께 즐거운 시간을 보내는 소녀의 모습을 빤히 지켜 보았다. "
    "I watched the girl having a good time with the cat intently. "

# game/chapter4.rpy:3503
translate english ecg9_label_ab9761fa:

    # "그 장면을 담아낼 수 있는 방법이 기억밖에 없다는 것이 못내 아쉽게 느껴질 정도였다. "
